Miramax Licenses Film Library to Hulu for Streaming in Japan

-- B y   R o b   G o l u m
-- 
2011-09-28T01:22:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/miramax-licenses-film-library-to-hulu-for-streaming-in-japan.html
Miramax, the closely held owner of
films such as “Shakespeare in Love,” reached a multiyear
agreement to provide its films to Hulu LLC subscribers in  Japan .  Beginning immediately, Hulu subscribers in Japan will be
able to instantly watch Miramax movies on Internet-connected
TVs, Blu-ray players and and game consoles, in addition to PCs,
tablets and smartphones,  Santa Monica , California-based Miramax
said today in a statement. Financial terms weren’t disclosed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Golum at 
 rgolum@bloomberg.net  